title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: New Declasse Impaler SZ Sedan
content:
Don’t judge a book by its cover at the next red light … the Declasse Impaler SZ may look like a completely forgettable sedan, but it’s what’s on the inside that counts: a frighteningly tunable V8 that just so happens to be an all-star of the Los Santos drag race circuit.

Available now at Southern San Andreas Super Autos.
